Format the Category buttons on the KPI Dashboard page 54

Step 1: Format the Category buttons on the KPI Dashboard page

-          - Select the Non Graded category image. Go to action and turn on, choose a bookmark and then select Non Graded HW

-          - Select the Graded category image. Go to action and turn on, choose a bookmark and then select Graded HW

-          - Select the Grader’s Quality image. Go to action and turn on, choose a bookmark and then select Grader’s Quality HW.
